---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
    title="About"
    description="Learn how GraceSoft approaches web development with clarity, scalable systems, UX thinking, and long-term reliability."
>
    <main class="about-page">
        <section class="title-section about-hero relative isolate overflow-hidden text-white px-4 py-20 sm:py-24 lg:py-28">
            <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-5 text-center reveal rise">
                <h1 class="sr-only">About</h1>
                <p class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight sm:text-4xl lg:text-6xl">Building Systems That Are Clear, Scalable, and Built to Last</p>
                <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-sm text-gs-purple-100 sm:text-base lg:text-xl">GraceSoft is a digital solutions studio focused on designing and developing modern web applications with a strong emphasis on structure, usability, and long-term reliability.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-problem-section px-4 py-14 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
            <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl space-y-6 sm:space-y-8">
                <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-center reveal rise">Too Many Systems Are Built Without Thinking</h2>
                <div class="feature-card reveal rise delay-1 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-4">
                    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gs-black-800">Many digital products today are rushed into development without proper planning, resulting in systems that are difficult to use, hard to maintain, and costly to scale.</p>
                    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gs-black-800">What starts as a simple idea often becomes a tangled system of patches, workarounds, and technical debt.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-philosophy-section px-4 py-14 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
            <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl space-y-6 sm:space-y-8">
                <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-center reveal rise">A Better Way to Build</h2>
                <div class="feature-card reveal rise delay-1 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-4">
                    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gs-black-800">At GraceSoft, we believe that good software starts with clarity.</p>
                    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gs-black-800">Instead of jumping straight into development, we take the time to understand the problem, design the system thoughtfully, and build with long-term scalability in mind.</p>
                    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gs-black-800">Every decision - from user flows to system architecture - is made with intention.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-focus-section px-4 py-14 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
            <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl space-y-8 sm:space-y-10">
                <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-center reveal rise">What We Focus On</h2>
                <div class="grid gap-4 sm:gap-5 grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3">
                    <article class="process-step reveal rise delay-1 text-center space-y-3">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold sm:text-xl">Intuitive UX</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gs-black-700">Designing intuitive user experiences</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="process-step reveal rise delay-2 text-center space-y-3">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold sm:text-xl">Modern Web Apps</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gs-black-700">Building modern, scalable web applications</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="process-step reveal rise delay-3 text-center space-y-3">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold sm:text-xl">Future-Ready Systems</h3>
                        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gs-black-700">Structuring systems that are maintainable and future-ready</p>
                    </article>
                </div>
                <p class="text-center text-base sm:text-lg text-gs-black-800 reveal rise delay-3">Whether you are starting from scratch or improving an existing system, the goal is the same: build it right.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-founder-section px-4 py-14 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
            <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-6 sm:space-y-8 text-center">
                <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl reveal rise">Meet the Founder</h2>
                <div class="feature-card reveal rise delay-1 space-y-4">
                    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gs-black-800">GraceSoft is founded by a full-stack web developer with over 8 years of experience in building and maintaining web applications.</p>
                    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gs-black-800">With a background that spans development, UX design, and cybersecurity, the approach combines technical expertise with a deep understanding of users and systems.</p>
                    <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gs-black-800">This multidisciplinary perspective allows GraceSoft to deliver solutions that are not only functional, but also thoughtful, secure, and scalable.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-credibility-section px-4 py-14 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
            <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-6 sm:space-y-8">
                <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-center reveal rise">Experience &amp; Background</h2>
                <ul class="about-credentials reveal rise delay-1">
                    <li>8+ years in web development</li>
                    <li>Experience across frontend and backend technologies</li>
                    <li>Completed Data Analytics training by Boston Consulting Group (BCG) with distinction</li>
                    <li>Course subjects include SQL, Python, and Machine Learning</li>
                    <li>Interviewed by BCG to provide input for an AI-powered career tool they are building</li>
                    <li>Certified in UX Design (Vertical Institute)</li>
                    <li>Trained in Cybersecurity</li>
                    <li>Award-winning project (SPINNOVEX Gold)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-section px-4 py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24">
            <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl space-y-6 sm:space-y-8 text-center cta-panel reveal rise">
                <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl leading-tight sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">Let us Build Something Meaningful</h2>
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg">If you are looking for a thoughtful, structured approach to building your next digital product, GraceSoft is here to help.</p>
                <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg">Let us start with a conversation.</p>
                <p>
                    <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-gs-purple-700 bg-white rounded-md px-5 py-3 shadow-sm transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:opacity-90">Start a Project &rarr;</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>